{"tid":745374,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"轉行既難度系數 我比滿分","createTime":"2018-07-16T16:41:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T04:04:04.000Z","uid":65119,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e7e5f872326d7befe6a8490c1ac50d49d8c5d9ed","tid":745374,"uid":65119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T16:41:18.000Z","msg":"本身做緊酒店狗既我終於忍唔住決定要轉行，決定邊搵工邊做狗，但係搵工真係好唔容易，大家點樣說服老細請張想轉行既白紙？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見到隔離po講緊有咩慘過番1500-0000，有呀！真係有！<br />\n1400-0000、1600-0200、2200-0800、0600-0400等等，仲未計ot<br />\n<br />\n因為好多酒店都係番10個鐘甚至10個半鐘，而食飯都未必有一個鐘⋯見到有舊同學做某旺角酒店，番10個半鐘得45分鐘食飯，食完飯想食支煙都要趕頭趕命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實我聽到都想幫佢搵工轉行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好想轉行求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c26154c8dada597bbac388c4f6dbd6968db0350f","tid":745374,"uid":164266,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T16:42:49.000Z","msg":"唔可以搵間福利好d既酒店嗎"},{"pid":"abb342baa4ca25e28c5b90b20216b25de996f98a","tid":745374,"uid":65119,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c26154c8dada597bbac388c4f6dbd6968db0350f","tid":745374,"uid":164266,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T16:42:49.000Z","msg":"唔可以搵間福利好d既酒店嗎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T16:48:17.000Z","msg":"天下酒店一樣黑，自問做緊果間已經好過舊同學做緊果間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n從來無聽過同屆畢業同學做酒店做得開心，大家都係做左一兩年酒店 然後好多人就開始轉行"},{"pid":"38d9be7d9fd060ed06af72bddc28a4