真有心唔怕遲, 祝你早日脫苦海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T03:07:47.000Z","msg":"佢地轉行轉左咩？好難搵工呀"},{"pid":"f66d557e93c81b8e4f8156b112a54534d6e21fdd","tid":745374,"uid":172297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T04:02:25.000Z","msg":"好多呀, 紀律部隊又有, 保險又有, 會所又有, 物管又有, Sales又有<br />\n<br />\n其實睇你自己想要咩, 要錢定要時間, 坦白講做酒店大家都係捱住等bonus, 但私人時間就一定要取捨, 又好似返shift咁, 我試過連通1x日通到開始懷疑人生, 突然醒覺唔想再咁落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 健康都輸撚埋"},{"pid":"56e5bc839ecd9b6db746d1d11dfbcc8daaa01a40","tid":745374,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T04:03:10.000Z","msg":"轉去做會所助理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfec49dd82459ed907db2add25306fb1b7e7f8e8","tid":745374,"uid":42283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T04:04:04.000Z","msg":"其實咁捱得，去做海關入境處幾好<br />\n俾酒店調教完應付老屎忽無難度"}]}